ADDITIONAL TERMS - FAIR USE AND INTENDED PURPOSE

This software is intended exclusively for personal, non-commercial use to manage
metadata for legally-owned personal media libraries.

By using this software, you acknowledge and agree that:

1. This software is designed for HOME USE ONLY
2. Scraping is rate-limited to a maximum of 80 items per session
3. Commercial use, bulk scraping, or redistribution of scraped data is prohibited
4. You will respect the terms of service of all third-party websites
5. The authors do not endorse or encourage violation of copyright laws or
   terms of service of third-party websites

Use of this software for purposes other than personal home media library
management is a violation of these terms and is not permitted.
